Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是男生的打扮活動比較方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的部員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我都還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是新加入的部員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  今天開始這裡廢部了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這歌是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼時空  出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天文警部  胸大！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&HE4E4E4&\fnsimhei}瞄準星星！\N{\fs10}\N{\fs24}幻想愛的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的少年啊  你為什麼打扮成男生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的青春在閃耀著嗎  沒有隱藏真實的自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來脫吧  現在就脫  把真實的自己暴露出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樹少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊麗莎白  你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是傭人  所以脫衣服是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請閃開  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快給我放手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都幹了些什麼  這COS套件是金屬蒸鍍的  非常貴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家似乎很高興的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副部長  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長進來說天悶部要廢部了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊勢田部長  你回到天悶部來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經放棄這個部了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有受理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生會有在受理  我已經和這部沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊勢田學姐到去年為止都還是這的部員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎和大庭學姐發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我不承認沒進行什麼正經活動的天悶部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊勢田學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有在進行正經活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在提出廢部之前  要不要再次確認一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次確認？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此  一起來觀測星體怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位好孩子  天文警部胸大秀開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午飯做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}做多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很麻煩啊  今年保育園的抽選也沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是天文警部胸大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後這位是助手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\shad0}（女天文刑事  Honey）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女天文刑事  Honey
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是被穿上女裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\shad0}（沒有那種台詞！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個哪裡算是觀測天體了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩英雄秀的天悶部  果然應該被廢部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  觀測天體的話不入夜的話就沒法進行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  在入夜之前邀請你一起乘坐這個摩天輪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且  小孩子們都很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  這哪裡有在高興  完全沒有在看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著那些身影  會讓我們想起自己小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這裡開始回想的話  從故事的展開看來是不是太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那是距今十年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮尾  這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來試著抓我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻哈哈  蓮尾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}等等  等等啊結花醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉蓮實醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就沉迷於「現在不會有這種笨蛋情侶了吧」的遊戲中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有股很香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香味似乎在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪出來了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結花醬還是這麼膽小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,望遠鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要稍微看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被罵的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛的客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  擅自進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇和星星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們喜歡哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧呢  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用望遠鏡看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  沒法出外行走  在這裡看星星倒是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過最近一陣子連用天體望遠鏡看都做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨丈夫曾喜歡的這個小小的薔薇園我想保留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可也不知道能維持多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶  蓮實醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不打擾的話  我們還能再來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是很歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後然後  我們會代替奶奶找星星和照顧花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結花醬  我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮實醬身體不好  在那邊休息就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就替我去查一下星星的事  蓮實醬頭腦很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個是五車二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\shad0}※五車二（α Aur/御夫座α）:御夫座內最亮的一顆恆星\N並且是全天第11亮星  排在大角和織女之後  是北半球的第3亮星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對哦  五車二在那個上面  那個是畢宿五哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\shad0}※畢宿五（α Tau/金牛座α）:畢宿第五星\N是金牛座的主星  距離地球68光年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…真的啊  不愧是蓮實醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們來這裡已經四年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經非常熟悉星星了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天能很清楚地看到星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:09:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你們知道玫瑰星雲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰星雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖然這個小望遠鏡看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像這個薔薇一樣紅紅的很漂亮的星雲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰星雲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想看一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會幫你拍玫瑰星雲的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這辦法不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片的話貼在房間裡  隨時都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼才能拍到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼時空  出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an6\shad0\fnsimhei\b0\3c&H000000&\c&HFFFFFF&\move(-50,33,228,33,0,360)}恐懼獸nukonuko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nukonuko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子們全都要被nuko淹沒了nuko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}對對  我試了試貓咪減肥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  是被nuko淹沒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}那個好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  胸大  恐懼獸nukonuko出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  變裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天文警部胸大僅用0.1微秒完成變身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就來說明原理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是哪裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是左手的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是腳的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是胸部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼變裝期間  請欣賞精彩的廣告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大森莊子的  總之試著唱唱的環節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的大森老師（人）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐  恐懼  恐懼恐懼  哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐  恐懼  恐懼恐懼  哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\shad0}（電話留言錄音中…）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\shad0}（訊息  144條）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\shad0}（來電…大森莊子）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天文警部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了呢  胸大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼獸nukonuko  去幹掉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nukonuko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  女天文刑事honey  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nuko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女天文刑事Honey  殉職
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nukonukonuko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸大  你不試下被nuko淹沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢  你這變態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天文Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不發光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nukonuko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇  這真是很厲害的特攝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對  真的在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}說起來  今天很熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滅火滅火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}所謂的小陽春天氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下還是戰略性撤退啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差點就被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你們在玩英雄遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是正式的秀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊勢田部長  害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼  怎麼可能會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才只是展現氣勢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來各位  為什麼要特意用讓人害怕的紅色手電筒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓眼睛習慣黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是手電筒的光  也會妨礙看星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是部長  很瞭解嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以別這樣搞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  天文警部的布偶我忘拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要嚇我啊  你這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓老師好像很冷的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇得我渾身發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說冷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說過在和式廁所裡有紅色的臉會從胯下偷看的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過的是在截稿前趕稿過勞而住院的同人作家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在即賣會賣本之類的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊勢田學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼啊  難道說還有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼  沒注意到的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊勢田學姐在的那樹的旁邊似乎有些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊勢田部長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪  是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是這麼膽小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過無意識中跑到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管過多少年  還是記得路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:16:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借來了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶會很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  肯定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也這個年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我們受這裡的奶奶所託
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照顧薔薇和觀測天體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮實在哪呢  終於正式借到天文部的活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮實…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要在這裡觀測天體？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  從最初開始我就是這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  學姐  這行李是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  今天我的杜布派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪搞來這麼高端的器材  難道是偷的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然引起了點小火  不過事先領到工錢真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個英雄秀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為只是因為興趣而在搞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生會管理嚴格  沒法拿到足夠的經費才去打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,租來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼正式的機器真的會用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈伯太空望遠鏡我也會用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼從什麼開始拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要拍攝的星星已經決定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的時間的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好是那個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話這個這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不是這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能順利拍到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你以為我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是是  你會用對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看  拍好了  小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  副部長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  戶田山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊勢田部長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛拍到的照片  你要看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NGC2237  通稱玫瑰星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會幫你拍玫瑰星雲的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這辦法不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片的話貼在房間裡  隨時都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有忘記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  不過這也全靠戶田山同學的幫忙才辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢  說不定就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  沒有的話就去做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐們真是隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  原來都是我的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之  天悶部算是有一項活動成果了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說取消廢除天悶部了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  形狀和吉他一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉他星雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得想彈吉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天悶部被廢部了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們從明天開始搞輕音部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往英國的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是降到入間基地的C-130的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞樂隊去英國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆夫塔爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是法國
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德里安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是美國
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.66,0:24:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.09,0:24:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓老師變成機器人  再變成摩托車
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.25,0:24:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝擊性的三段變形
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.91,0:24:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DX貓老師  堂堂登場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.03,0:24:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\shad0\blur3\b0\c&HEFE4F0&\3c&H5A91CE&\pos(392,284)}下回「viva天」敬請期待！
