Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:02.97,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(100,50)}祈禱這份心動與愉悅能夠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.43,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(100,50)}不斷繼續
